---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<main class="px-8 py-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto font-mono text-neutral-100 bg-neutral-950 leading-relaxed">

  <h1 class="text-3xl mb-6">Media · The Groundative Way</h1>

  <p class="mb-6">
    The Groundative Tradition lives through direct speech and shared seeing.
    These recordings, dialogues, and transmissions form the public teaching field
    known as <strong>The Groundative Way</strong> — where philosophy becomes voice.
  </p>

  <section class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl mb-4">Teaching Series</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      A growing collection of spoken teachings and reflections by XYNACT,
      presenting the laws, methods, and living practice of the Groundative Tradition.
    </p>
    <div class="aspect-video mb-4">
      <!-- Replace with your YouTube or Rumble embed -->
      <iframe
        class="w-full h-80 border border-neutral-800"
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/"
        title="Groundative Teaching"
        frameborder="0"
        allowfullscreen>
      </iframe>
    </div>
    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@XYNACT" target="_blank"
       class="px-5 py-2 border border-neutral-700 text-neutral-100 hover:bg-neutral-800 transition">
       Visit Channel · YouTube
    </a>
  </section>

  <hr class="border-neutral-800 my-10"/>

  <section class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl mb-4">Dialogues · Interviews</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Conversations between XYNACT and other thinkers, artists, and practitioners —
      exploring presence, art, and the re-grounding of knowledge.
    </p>
    <div class="aspect-video mb-4">
      <iframe
        class="w-full h-80 border border-neutral-800"
        src="https://rumble.com/embed/"
        title="Groundative Dialogue"
        frameborder="0"
        allowfullscreen>
      </iframe>
    </div>
    <a href="https://rumble.com/c/XYNACT" target="_blank"
       class="px-5 py-2 border border-neutral-700 text-neutral-100 hover:bg-neutral-800 transition">
       Visit Channel · Rumble
    </a>
  </section>

  <hr class="border-neutral-800 my-10"/>

  <section class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl mb-4">Audio · Podcast</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Selected talks and readings in audio form — a quieter field for listening
      and reflection.
    </p>
    <audio controls class="w-full border border-neutral-800">
      <source src="/media/sample.mp3" type="audio/mpeg"/>
      Your browser does not support the audio element.
    </audio>
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mt-2">
      <em>“Presence before proposition.”</em>
    </p>
  </section>

  <hr class="border-neutral-800 my-10"/>

  <section>
    <h2 class="text-2xl mb-4">Upcoming · The Groundative Way Live</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Live dialogues, workshops, and field transmissions will begin once the
      public teaching cycle opens.  Streams and schedules will appear here.
    </p>
  </section>

  <footer class="mt-12 text-xs text-neutral-600 text-center">
    © 2025 XYNACT · What Is, Is · Groundative Tradition
  </footer>
</main>
